metadata.description:

Disclaimer: The NFT being offered is a digital asset with no real-world value or rights. Any resemblances to real people and events are purely coincidental. The NFT is being sold (minted) as-is, with no warranties or representations. The seller (Set in Series) shall not be liable for any damages or loss arising from the purchase or use of the NFT.
